1#pragma once
2#include <QtCore/QUuid>
3#include <utility>
4namespace QtNodes
5{
6 enum class PortType
7 {
8 None,
9 In,
10 Out
11 };
12 static const int INVALID = -1;
13 using PortIndex = int;
14 struct Port
15 {
16 PortType type;
17 PortIndex index;
18 Port() : type(PortType::None), index(INVALID)
19 {
20 }
21 Port(PortType t, PortIndex i) : type(t), index(i)
22 {
23 }
24 bool indexIsValid()
25 {
26 return index != INVALID;
27 }
28 bool portTypeIsValid()
29 {
30 return type != PortType::None;
31 }
32 };
33 // using PortAddress = std::pair<QUuid, PortIndex>;
34 inline PortType oppositePort(PortType port)
35 {
36 PortType result = PortType::None;
37 switch (port)
38 {
39 case PortType::In: result = PortType::Out; break;
40 case PortType::Out: result = PortType::In; break;
41 default: break;
42 }
43 return result;
44 }
45} // namespace QtNodes
